			"MinV35", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V18], TRUE),
			"MinV36", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V19], TRUE),
			"MinTemplateIdColumnRole4", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TemplateIdColumnRole], TRUE)
		)

EVALUATE
	GENERATEALL(
		KEEPFILTERS(ROW(
			"Placeholder", BLANK()
		)),
		GENERATEALL(
			KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_0),
			GENERATEALL(
				KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_1),
				GENERATEALL(
					KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_2),
					__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_3
				)
			)
		)
	)

DEFINE
	VAR __H0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Corporativo"}, 'Vendas'[Segmento])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Vendas'[Fabricantes],
			"SumValorVenda", CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda])),
			"VendasSumValorVenda", IGNORE(
				CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda]), KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [SumValorVenda], 0, 'Vendas'[Fabricantes], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[SumValorVenda] DESC, 'Vendas'[Fabricantes]

DEFINE
	VAR __H0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Corporativo"}, 'Vendas'[Segmento])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Vendas'[Categoria],
			"SumValorVenda", CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda])),
			"VendasSumValorVenda", IGNORE(
				CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda]), KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [SumValorVenda], 0, 'Vendas'[Categoria], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SumValorVenda] DESC, 'Vendas'[Categoria]

metrics.visualTitle: Soma de ValorVenda por Categoria e Loja

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Vendas'[Categoria],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Vendas'[Loja], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			"SumValorVenda", CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Vendas'[Categoria]", 'Vendas'[Categoria],
			"'Vendas'[Loja]", 'Vendas'[Loja],
			"SumValorVenda", [SumValorVenda]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Vendas'[Categoria]", 'Vendas'[Categoria],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [SumValorVenda]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Vendas'[Categoria]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(201, __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns, [SortBy_DM0_0], 0, 'Vendas'[Categoria], 1)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Vendas'[Loja])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Vendas'[Loja], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Vendas'[Loja],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Vendas'[Loja]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Vendas'[Categoria], [ColumnIndex]

metrics.visualTitle: Total de Valor Venda por Estado e Vendedor

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __ValueFilterI0 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
					'Vendas'[Estado],
					'Vendas'[Vendedor],
					"SumValorVenda", CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda]))
				)
			),
			[SumValorVenda] > 30000
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Vendas'[Estado],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Vendas'[Vendedor], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__ValueFilterI0,
			"SumValorVenda", CALCULATE(SUM('Vendas'[ValorVenda]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Vendas'[Estado]", 'Vendas'[Estado],
			"'Vendas'[Vendedor]", 'Vendas'[Vendedor],
			"SumValorVenda", [SumValorVenda]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Vendas'[Estado])

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Vendas'[Estado]", 'Vendas'[Estado],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [SumValorVenda]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Vendas'[Vendedor])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 1,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'Vendas'[Estado],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Vendas'[Vendedor], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0Primary,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Vendas'[Vendedor],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Vendas'[Vendedor]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Vendas'[Estado], [ColumnIndex]
